Brazil's Child Preachers

Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Seyi Rhodes, published by Channel 4 broadcasted as part of CH4 Unreported World series in 2015 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/5/56/Brazil-s-Child-Preachers-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Reporter Seyi Rhodes and director Mike Healy meet some of Brazil's newest celebrities: child preachers who attract large crowds who believe the children are in direct contact with God and that some can even perform miracles and cure the sick. Unreported World highlights how these child preachers are at the forefront of the country's fast-growing evangelical movement, which is gaining religious and political power.
